                     <interp inst="t18281204-199-person1686" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, and produce the ribbons.</p>
               <p>Five witnesses gave the prisoner a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 15.</p>
